Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.39,0:00:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,晨报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,又……又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,纯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那本书绝对不能打开
